Process called "load_utility_builtins" that takes ctx as BashSemanticContext returns Nothing:
    Note: Load utility built-in commands

    Let utility_commands be a list containing:
        create_bash_command with "cd" and "change directory" and true,
        create_bash_command with "pwd" and "print working directory" and true,
